snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Chaos Gate - Daemonhunters | Accolades Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1611910/Warhammer_40000_Chaos_Gate__Daemonhunters/ 
Lead humanity’s greatest weapon, the Grey Knights, in this fast-paced turn-based tactical RPG: Warhammer 40,000: Chaos Gate – Daemonhunters. Root out and purge a galaxy-spanning plague across multiple worlds, using the tactics and talents of your own personalised squad of Daemonhunters. 
Out now on PC.

Find out more at www.chaosgate.com
